# Fintech Payment Gateway (Flask)

This is a simple fintech payment gateway simulation built using Flask.

## Features
- Payment API (`POST /pay`)
- Input validation
- Unique transaction ID generation
- Idempotency support (prevents duplicate charges)
- Basic logging for transactions
- Simulated payment success/failure

## How to Run

1. Install dependencies:
```bash
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
